{"tid":1807142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"捉完鬼捉中手足 逼到人除罩倒曬袋啲出黎 仲要唔比人走話人地逃離不果？","createTime":"2020-01-01T16:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T17:05:05.000Z","uid":65210,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3cf904776a413be867d635ce0724759e658159b4","tid":1807142,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:08:45.000Z","msg":"捉鬼捉到手足<br />\n逼到手足係幾十個鏡頭前除口罩 <br />\n倒曬野落地下任人check<br />\n發現捉錯咗就同其他市民講唔好再捉鬼？？？<br />\n除曬罩 check曬袋又唔比人走<br />\n話人地逃離現場不果 到底係乜野事<br />\n捉錯手足唔放人走 仲要用逃離形容佢地<br />\n呢兩個手足比班捉鬼撚害死啦！！<br />\n以後做野都唔方便<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再捉鬼啦<br />\n防鬼 不捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n鬼係捉唔完㗎 <br />\n學堂出黎啲長頭髮文青後生女狗<br />\n大媽Type 老狗<br />\n要擺臥底狗跟本就唔會捉得曬 <br />\n唔係隻隻狗都係大大隻隻咁<br />\n2019運動開始就話全民建身練跑<br />\n到手足練到大大隻隻夠隻揪<br />\n又用身形捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一旦開始捉鬼 <br />\n只會瓦解成場運動嘅信任</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a0VA9Rn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa0VA9Rn.png&h=f72b74fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MqFaeh2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMqFaeh2.png&h=e09b7d0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n//捉鬼嘅害處，可簡單概括為三點：<br />\n 1. 分散手足注意力<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\">2. 互相猜疑，瓦解信任<br />\n 3. 捉錯鬼，曝露手足身份//</span><br />\n<br />\n捉鬼最大嘅成本係捉錯鬼<br />\n捉鬼最大嘅成本係捉錯鬼<br />\n捉鬼最大嘅成本係捉錯鬼<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">前線手足好可能因為捉鬼而失去數以年計嘅自由甚至冇命，</span></span><br />\n曱甴最想我哋捉鬼！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"071f6d45e65847414724b75ebd609c4160d9b059","tid":1807142,"uid":42007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:11:15.000Z","msg":"我係狗真係好開心，見到你地捉鬼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1807138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1807138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a78830117a73694caab847cf2187d2f15fe462e0","tid":1807142,"uid":25379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:11:16.000Z","msg":"我都曾經被人當鬼咁捉，但我冇介意過"},{"pid":"37982aef5828d7308d8251a6596b5ed1b71f0c56","tid":1807142,"uid":34217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:12:38.000Z","msg":"捉鬼真係好on9..."},{"pid":"b6101fe603df6317fb96bd1113d6a85812949ed5","tid":1807142,"uid":37673,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a78830117a73694caab847cf2187d2f15fe462e0","tid":1807142,"uid":25379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:11:16.000Z","msg":"我都曾經被人當鬼咁捉，但我冇介意過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:13:05.000Z","msg":"你唔介意唔代表人哋唔會"},{"pid":"3857cd485ccdd27c930929583e1e8eeb8c3ae56f","tid":1807142,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:13:42.000Z","msg":"仆街出晒樣肯定好高風險<br />\nDLLM有冇即場道歉呀"},{"pid":"5d442436f83afb93b9899e52f179a1e062ef83db","tid":1807142,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:14:04.000Z","msg":"唔好捉鬼啦,真係驚鬼可以跟住佢,未現身唔好捉,好易捉錯手足,我都幫手驗過真係feel到手足果種被誤解既痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f3b5fc4c2838e126e40020335472190c165f09","tid":1807142,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:14:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4dc3de840c8a1b46329d110a09722794848e52e","tid":1807142,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a78830117a73694caab847cf2187d2f15fe462e0","tid":1807142,"uid":25379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:11:16.000Z","msg":"我都曾經被人當鬼咁捉，但我冇介意過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:15:43.000Z","msg":"你係咪裝完修先? 人地而家出晒樣好易比人拉架<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee49e610de5d914d90f9b7cb3f5f35ddfacef34f","tid":1807142,"uid":65210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wBUyb8q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwBUyb8q.png&h=7be6e740&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2237719da24e28ddb5ef4b2160a2a195deb01cf6","tid":1807142,"uid":25379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6101fe603df6317fb96bd1113d6a85812949ed5","tid":1807142,"uid":37673,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a78830117a73694caab847cf2187d2f15fe462e0","tid":1807142,"uid":25379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:11:16.000Z","msg":"我都曾經被人當鬼咁捉，但我冇介意過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:13:05.000Z","msg":"你唔介意唔代表人哋唔會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:16:47.000Z","msg":"攝返衫，show 個袋被其中一個手足睇，罩都唔使除，我明有乜問題<br />\n<br />\n當然，如果要我除面罩，咁我可能會介意嘅"},{"pid":"7e76fe9ded56b0f47a7f8b24245fac34c4a29155","tid":1807142,"uid":25379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4dc3de840c8a1b46329d110a09722794848e52e","tid":1807142,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a78830117a73694caab847cf2187d2f15fe462e0","tid":1807142,"uid":25379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:11:16.000Z","msg":"我都曾經被人當鬼咁捉，但我冇介意過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:15:43.000Z","msg":"你係咪裝完修先? 人地而家出晒樣好易比人拉架<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:18:46.000Z","msg":"我唔係，不過個人高大，有時被人誤會，<br />\n當然，裝修完係難搞啲嘅"},{"pid":"debf78ab90dd048df1ed8af8732f1416f9371974","tid":1807142,"uid":105738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:20:57.000Z","msg":"其實我真係唔知捉乜撚野鬼"},{"pid":"18b8a872cd34383e907980b917a68d3b50b0eda8","tid":1807142,"uid":6033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:22:28.000Z","msg":"點解唔應該捉鬼<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eHNfdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eHNfdS</a>"},{"pid":"f72a43762e7c31d3faeb21a779fe5f110c4847e3","tid":1807142,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:25:42.000Z","msg":"比你地係捉到鬼又點<br />\n又唔撚係打<br />\n又唔撚係殺<br />\n我係個兩個手足就心淡 <br />\n咁多鏡頭下都比人逼到要除罩<br />\n之後仲點做野<br />\n一日未摵走鋪捉鬼癮 <br />\n勇武出黎都有機會比自己友篤返出黎"},{"pid":"a5e27dc628d34f38a9863c7ba6064f3ab6f13cd8","tid":1807142,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:28:16.000Z","msg":"講真，捉到真係鬼你惡得出樣咩<br />\n<br />\n咪又係屌下佢老母叫死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後咪又係成班狂暴衝過黎鳩打鳩拉"},{"pid":"051238c445cbe11e7d4394a63957989876bd28be","tid":1807142,"uid":103363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:29:26.000Z","msg":"捉鬼真係會玩死自己友<br />\n唔好再捉喇<br />\n有狗嗰陣又唔打<br />\n冇狗嗰陣又係咁捉<br />\n好喇比你捉到喇<br />\n隻狗一拎枝辣椒出黎又淆<br />\n咁捉黎做乜鳩<br />\n除非你話佢無啦啦裝修黃店亂咁打人咁就話姐<br />\n<br />\n裝修師傅嘅我信佢地唔會無啦啦亂生事端增加自己比狗咬嘅風險"},{"pid":"f69438d90b4f947277aa16bf46044543b10ed066","tid":1807142,"uid":282886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:30:29.000Z","msg":"其實如果係鬼仲唔走咩<br />\n留係現場今時今日真係收屍都似<br />\n之前見到有兩個好似鬼，其他人都覺去問<br />\n結果國泰黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af24829d4bf76232966cedbec623cef57e16fa46","tid":1807142,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3cf904776a413be867d635ce0724759e658159b4","tid":1807142,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:08:45.000Z","msg":"捉鬼捉到手足<br />\n逼到手足係幾十個鏡頭前除口罩 <br />\n倒曬野落地下任人check<br />\n發現捉錯咗就同其他市民講唔好再捉鬼？？？<br />\n除曬罩 check曬袋又唔比人走<br />\n話人地逃離現場不果 到底係乜野事<br />\n捉錯手足唔放人走 仲要用逃離形容佢地<br />\n呢兩個手足比班捉鬼撚害死啦！！<br />\n以後做野都唔方便<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再捉鬼啦<br />\n防鬼 不捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n鬼係捉唔完㗎 <br />\n學堂出黎啲長頭髮文青後生女狗<br />\n大媽Type 老狗<br />\n要擺臥底狗跟本就唔會捉得曬 <br />\n唔係隻隻狗都係大大隻隻咁<br />\n2019運動開始就話全民建身練跑<br />\n到手足練到大大隻隻夠隻揪<br />\n又用身形捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一旦開始捉鬼 <br />\n只會瓦解成場運動嘅信任</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br 